description:
A 16-episode journey through the story of The Pilgrim's Progress. Part 9 of 16. Christian again  finds himself in the dark. Emerging from the forest, he barely makes it into the Palace Beautiful where he meets other faithful Christians. There he receives needed encouragement, and is  clothed with the armor of God for the task ahead… 

A production of RevelationMedia, based on John Bunyan’s masterpiece, this powerful allegory will help families face the trials and temptations of the Christian Life. RevelationMedia is committed to providing quality Christian content to the US and the ends of the earth for FREE. Donate today to support the distribution and translation of content like The Pilgrim’s Progress today at www.RevelationMedia.com 

Director: Robert Fernandez
Starring: John Rhys-Davies, Ben Price,  Kristyn Getty, David Thorpe 
Executive Producer: Steve Cleary
